description: Redevelopment of site to provide a total of 58 affordable housing and shared ownership residential units within 2 x part 2-storey, part 4-storey blocks (block A and E), a 4-storey block (block C) and two part 2, part 3-storey terraces (Block B and D) comprising 6 x 3 bed and 8 x 4 bed houses, 14 x 1 bed, 26 x 2 bed and 4 x 3 bed self contained flats with associated surface car parking, covered cycle parking, play area and ancillary works.
